  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Kinder Finders</i> is a click and find game featuring hand drawn characters, items and locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game you are the newest member of the Kinder Finders (an after school club all about helping people). And the Kinder Finders are all about <strong>BADGES</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Talk to people all around town. Help them find things. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And with your <strong>kindness</strong>,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And your <strong>findness,</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn some badges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479300/extras/49b4de41e548f028e1b39ada44d46e79.avif?t=1756147683\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Everyone Needs Some Kindness</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is full of characters who have all lost things. Can you help them?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 unique locations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >33 quests </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >33 badges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15-20+ Items to find in each location</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 Cozy Songs to vibe with</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All with original art created by Patrick Sutherland (Art By Sutherland).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring the musical talents of DJ Kenneth A. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >*NEW REMIX MODE*</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the original five levels again with brand new item locations. A New Character: Remi X and a fun seek and find for Remi themself! Turns the original game into a brand new experience of finding. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And its a free update.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479300/extras/4198670ee49fb39144a6c48ff1ad8d4e.avif?t=1756147683\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BADGES! BADGES! BADGES!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479300/extras/ae5d6d4e56f09ae8732fc93c2f9ea19e.avif?t=1756147683\" width=616 height=300 /></span></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Kinder Finders</i> is a click and find game featuring hand drawn characters, items and locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game you are the newest member of the Kinder Finders (an after school club all about helping people). And the Kinder Finders are all about <strong>BADGES</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Talk to people all around town. Help them find things. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And with your <strong>kindness</strong>,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And your <strong>findness,</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn some badges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479300/extras/49b4de41e548f028e1b39ada44d46e79.avif?t=1756147683\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Everyone Needs Some Kindness</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is full of characters who have all lost things. Can you help them?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 unique locations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >33 quests </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >33 badges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15-20+ Items to find in each location</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 Cozy Songs to vibe with</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All with original art created by Patrick Sutherland (Art By Sutherland).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring the musical talents of DJ Kenneth A. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >*NEW REMIX MODE*</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the original five levels again with brand new item locations. A New Character: Remi X and a fun seek and find for Remi themself! Turns the original game into a brand new experience of finding. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And its a free update.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img cla